passages.text: GS Materials Sept 2....Gold ATH, PGM cover, Iron ore chops the range, Parade Blue, Steel meh and the Copper forward
高盛材料- 9月2日......黄金创历史新高，PGM回补，铁矿石区间震荡，阅兵蓝，钢铁平淡，铜价前瞻
DXY 97.84 CNH 7.14 10YR 4.25 Gold 3485 Copper 9883 Oil 68.44
DXY 97.84人民币离岸价7.14 10年期国债收益率4.25黄金3485铜9883原油68.44

Some days you run straight at the defensive line, others you drift sideways looking for a gap....Pass overnight, did what you expect it to do, Golds up, Uranium pulls back, as BHP remains strong in ASX I am watching The Military "Parade Blue" in China tomorrow...Iron Ore bang in the middle of the range we keep flagging, Consumer buying at \(\) 100\(and producer hedging at\) \ \(105\) . Mill margins remains positive and hot metal prodn strong, expect some cuts this week, however will pick back up fast. Some eyeballing Indian export policy, talk of potential low grade export tariffs (October) that could support seaborne mkt tightness (I am pretty sceptical of this). Last point is feedback that CTA are in the top quartile, approaching max long (flipped long from \(\) 96\(upwards, that's 8 weeks of buying, so makes sense they approaching that level). We can kind of guess why BHP trades where it does (low vol result, safe haven, rotation from Aussie big cap drawdown), however the comment I liked yday was "BHP has the multiple you would expect of the RIO story and RIO the BHP story". That really revolves around the 5yr growth picture. Perhaps the mkt is embedding a multiple put into BHP for capital returns? The type nergy gets. I don't see it myself, but happy to be convinced otherwise...VALT LN, no placing? Stocks traded great yday, lockup expired, no one sees it as strategic for AAL (as articulated), its as well seasoned as a Sunday Roast at 2pm, commodity price trades in sympathy of the precious space, NPH results last week missed on the prodn forward...IMP/NPH/SSW all rallied c.10% as short base is chunky. Lets the whites of your eyes over the next few days ... Watching Energy as Bessent comments around sanctions and US position Link, nothing new, just "all option on the table", have seen a persistent fade in energy vol, they use the phrase "max short" on positioning, however tight fundamental balances keep the price elevated, saw a few covers off equity shorts yesterday, just tactical trading, EQNR and ENI the big shorts, feel more comfortable adding some risk in EQNR and SHEL is the quality proxy that

lets you sleep at night.... Corporates continue to take actions, have seen a lotin metal smelting, closing cahs burning assets, MT looking to close SA steel, GLEN looking at Ferrochrome business (those two are today stories, there will be more tomorrow). Just tightens balances over time.

有些日子你会直冲防线，有些日子你会侧向寻找突破口......隔夜走势如预期，黄金上涨，铀价回落，而BHP在澳交所依然坚挺。我在关注明天中国的“阅兵蓝”......铁矿石正好处于我们一直提示的区间中部，消费者在100美元买入，生产商在105美元套保。钢厂利润率依然为正，热金属产量强劲，预计本周会有一些减产，但会很快恢复。一些人关注印度出口政策，有传言称可能在10月对低品位矿征收出口关税，这可能支撑海运市场的紧张（对此我相信怀疑）。最后一点反馈是CTA处于前四分位，接近最大多头仓位（从96美元开始转多至今，已连续买入8周，所以接近该水平是合理的）。我们大致可以猜到BHP的交易位置原因（低波动业绩、安全避风港、从澳洲大盘股回撤中轮换），不过我昨天喜欢的一句评论是：“BHP的估值倍数像RIO的故事，而RIO的估值倍数像BHP的故事”。这实际上围绕着未来5年的增长前景。或许市场正在为BHP的资本回报预期嵌入一个估值保护？这种能量类型我自己没看出来，但乐意被说服......VALT LN，没有配股？股票昨天交易表现很好，锁定期已到期，没有人认为这对AAL有战略意义（如所述），就像周日下午两点的烤肉一样老练，商品价格与贵金属板块联动交易，NPH上周的业绩在产量指引上未达预期......IMP/NPH/SSW都因空头仓位较大而上涨了约 \(10\%\) 。接下来几天盯紧点看......关注能源板块，因为Bessent对制裁和美国立场的评论（链接），没什么新内容，只是“所有选项都在桌面上”，能源波动率持续回落，他们用“max short”来形容仓位，但紧张的基本面平衡让价格维持高位，昨天看到一些股票空头回补，只是战术性交易，EQNR和ENI是主要空头，在EQNR上加点风险感觉更舒服，而SHEL是让你晚上睡得着的优质替代品......企业继续采取行动，在金属冶炼领域看到很多关闭烧钱资产的情况，MT计划关闭南非钢铁业务，GLEN在考虑铬铁业务（这两个是今天的新闻，明天还会有更多）。只是随着时间推移逐渐收紧平衡。

Centrica - 1yr life extension at 2 nuclear plants in UK (Heysham 1 and Hartlepool) which will now continue until March 28. Which will add 3 TWhr of volumes (presumably in 27- 28). Small +ve; stock is probably "least bad" (along with NG/) of the UK utes which are now a popular short into the Autumn budget
Centrica——英国两座核电站（Heysham 1和Hartlepool）延长1年寿命，将运营至2028年3月。这将增加3太瓦时的发电量（推测在2027- 2028年）。小幅利好；该股可能是英国公用事业公司中“相对最不差”的（与NG/一起），目前这些公司在秋季预算前已成为热门做空标的。

Gold - commod sales published a few thoughts yday Link to note. Talking to trading: has had a 6month consolidation, lot of the mkt drifted out of it. Lots were arguing break support lowernow the mkt is cleansed, run out of sellers, nothing obvious on Friday, momo picked up the \(3450 level taken out, Asia steps in to buy,\) 3500 is a big level, are we at a point where short term money tries to fade again? However the trend takes us higher and we chase it into year end. Key event is obv Week end payrolls and front end rates, if weak we build proper momemtum. On the Vol side we have been at the lows of 13 and now trades back to 17.5. They liked owning topside and outrights, even after the move they still like upside. Remains bullish, client interest picking up, it' s a high conviction long for trading. CHASE. ...I mentioned yday the interest in FRES, HOC, I know EDV in London is printing cash
but like a lot of these names the sovereign risk argument was a discussion yday, its real and the mkt is complacent. West Africa, Mali, Mozambique, Guinea....

黄金——商品销售昨天发布了一些想法，附上笔记链接。与交易部门交流：已经经历了6个月的盘整，很多市场参与者已经退出。很多人曾争论是否跌破支撑位，但现在市场已经被清洗，卖方耗尽，周五没有明显变化，动能开始增强， \(\) 3450\(被突破，亚洲买盘介入，\) \ \(3500\) 是一个重要关口，我们是否到了短期资金再次尝试做空的时点？然而趋势推动我们走高，并在年底前追涨。关键事件显然是本周末的非农就业数据和短端利率，如果数据疲软，我们将积累真正的动能。在波动率方面，我们此前处于13的低位，现在回升至17.5。他们喜欢持有上方期权和直接多头，即便在行情走高之后，他们依然看好上行。依然看多，客户兴趣回升，这是交易中高信心的多头。追涨。....我昨天提到对FRES、HOC的兴趣，我知道伦敦的EDV正在大量赚钱，但像很多此类公司一样，昨天讨论了主权风险的问题，这是真实存在的，而市场却掉以轻心。西非、马里、莫桑比克、几内亚....

Copper - good note commods sales (link) on why Comex trades at a premium, the arb today (+ \(\) 80/0.8\%\$ , goes to \(\) 420/4\%\(into early 2026), where to from here... Feeds a little on the comments I mentioned earlier about stranded tonnes. 2H "refined" metal availability is key for price. Franchise has seen signs of trend following money re- engage (recall last week the "vol compression" views....so the work use of emergence is very early days). I see some positional data suggesting 5year lows SXPP, doesn't change how it trades...Equally i see Copper gap up, get sold, its that vol compression. Needs a catalyst. Next update i am expecting is IVN.CN on Kakula, guided for Sept so watch the tape here.

铜——有一篇不错的商品销售笔记（链接）解释了为什么Comex交易存在溢价，今天的套利（+80美元/0.8%，到2026年初升至420美元/4%），接下来会怎样....这与我之前提到的关于滞留吨位的评论有些关联。下半年“精炼”金属的供应是价格的关键。业务部门已经看到趋势跟随型资金重新入场的迹象（回想上周的“波动率压缩”观点....所以这种迹象的出现还处于非常早期的阶段）。我看到一些持仓数据表明SXPP处于5年低点，但这并不改变它的交易方式....同样，我看到铜价跳空上涨后被抛售，这就是波动率压缩。需要一个催化剂。我预计的下一个更新是IVN.CN关于Kakula的消息，指引在9月，所以要关注这里的盘面。

Critical minerals - you had this headline later in day yday: France Asks EU to Build Stockpiles of Critical Raw Materials..have a listen to this one, minute 5 its gets interesting link, equity capital \(>50\%\) (66%) more expensive in DM v EM, debt capital cost even more stark. As they say, think about the capital intensity of the industry (I broached this yesterday also).
关键矿产——你昨天晚上时候有这样一个标题：法国要求欧盟建立关键原材料储备....听听这个，第5分钟开始变得有趣，链接显示，发达市场的股本资本成本比新兴市场高出50%以上（66%），债务资本成本差距更为显著。正如他们所说，想想这个行业的资本密集度（我昨天也提到过这一点）。

MT.NA - reading the EUR strategy note yday and me thinking about it, i know the reaction function to Ukraine peace deal climbdown is to sell the winners of that thematic....Fundamentally Its really a waiting game as to when you think volumes can recover. I have said all summer that the key for most investors is need to see volumes improve to give a signal price can follow. I know speaking to our steel traders: US conf last week (Atlanta), mood is dire (could argue should have been worse than it was), but its seasonal. Contracting season is starting, expect the outer months to get more interesting, US prices half the tariffs (ie 25% v 50%) and likely that we are over counting the risk of the Tariffs.... have seen CLF sign 2- 3 year fixed price deals (the price and the term is also ambiguous) ...Its as bad as you can get, the curve has \(\) 100\$ cost contagio, imports are priced out of the mkt basis the 50% tariff. Demand poor, inventory drifting back to the middle of the range. .... See GIR thoughts link...In EUR the picture looks better given CBAM, Quotas for 2026, can argue

the price looks cheap into 2026 if this happens and importers may not know the liability that they may carry basis the default rate...however its always a HOPE trade that it is going to get better. The note below is worth a read

MT.NA——昨天读了欧元策略报告并自己思考后，我知道对乌克兰和平协议回撤的反应机制是卖出该主题的赢家......从根本上说，这其实是一个等待的过程，关键在于你认为成交量何时能恢复。我整个夏天都在说，对大多数投资者来说，关键是需要看到成交量改善，才能发出价格可以跟随的信号。我和我们的钢铁交易员交流过：上周在美国的会议（亚特兰大），市场情绪很糟（甚至可以说本该更糟），但这是季节性因素。合同签订季节即将开始，预计远期月份会更有看头，美国价格是关税的一半（即 \(25\%\) 对比 \(50\%\) ），而且我们很可能高估了关税的风险......看到CLF签了2- 3年的固定价格合同（价格和期限也不明确）......情况糟到不能再糟，曲线呈现每吨100美元的远期升水，基于 \(50\%\) 关税，进口被排挤出市场。需求疲弱，库存回落到区间中部......请查看GIR观点链接......在欧元区，由于CBAM和2026年的配额，前景看起来更好，如果这些情况发生，可以认为价格在2026年前看起来很便宜，而且进口商可能并不了解他们可能基于默认费率所承担的责任......然而，这始终是一种寄希望于情况会好转的交易。下面的说明值得一读。

European investment opportunity - link - STOXX Europe P/E at 14.4x is in the 70th percentile of history (comped against other assets classes its one of least expensive), GIR see low positioning (especially by domestic investors), inexpensive valuation vs. other assets, and a growing desire to diversify away from US exposure (both due to dollar weakness and concentrated positions in Tech). Rolling forward our European index targets, we forecast 5% price and 8% total return over 12-months....GIR continue to advocate a mix of cyclicals and defensives with OWs in Banks, Telecoms, Tech and Retailers and UW in Autos, Chemicals and Energy....Come pretty interesting charts on positioning, Value v growth performance, cyclicals v defensives...See exhibit 16. Everyone continues to hate on materials, not saying that is wrong, just saying starting points matter.

欧洲投资机会 - 链接 - STOXX Europe 市盈率为 14.4 倍，处于历史的第 70 百分位（与其他资产类别相比，这是最便宜的之一），GIR 认为当前持仓水平较低（尤其是本土投资者），相较其他资产估值便宜，同时对分散美国敞口的需求不断增长（既由于美元走弱，也由于科技板块持仓过于集中）。在我们滚动更新的欧洲指数目标中，预计未来 12 个月价格上涨 5%，总回报 8%....GIR 继续建议周期股与防御股的组合，超配银行、电信、科技和零售，低配汽车、化工和能源......有一些关于持仓、价值与成长表现、周期股与防御股的非常有趣的图表......见图表 16。大家依然不看好原材料板块，不说这种看法是错的，只是起点很重要。
Source:GoldmanSachsGlobal InvestmentResearch
\*National Parade Tomorrow
Tomorrow we will witness the long discussed national parade. Latest agenda shows that it will last for 70 minutes and be composed of two parts: military formation and parade.
明天我们将迎来备受讨论的全国阅兵。最新议程显示，阅兵将持续70分钟，由两部分组成：军队列阵和阅兵式。
In terms of sectors, defense has seen profit taking kicked in while materials and chemicals have seen better momentum
从行业来看，国防板块出现了获利回吐，而材料和化工板块的动能表现更好

In terms of broad market impact, it's been long chatted that retail sentiment should hold at least until the event. While recent market has shown resilience, it's mainly led by telco/Al related news, yet still worth watching if the event could be used as excuse to profit take/on the other hand, there might also be some market nurturing measures around the event.
从整体市场影响来看，市场早已普遍认为零售投资者情绪至少会维持到活动结束。尽管近期市场表现出韧性，但主要是由电信/人工智能相关消息推动。不过仍值得关注的是，活动是否会被用作获利了结的借口；另一方面，活动期间也可能会有一些呵护市场的措施出台。

https://baijiahao.baidu.com/s?id=1842105948158818307&wfr=spider&for=pc \*Last week domestic equity ETFs recorded 8.7 billion yuan (\$1.2 billion) of net inflows, ending a nine week selling streak as we move into the military parade.
\*上周，国内股票型ETF录得87亿元人民币（12亿美元）净流入，结束了连续九周的净卖出趋势，正值我们进入阅兵阶段。
Still the size is moderate when comparing to national team activities: During the April selloff, equity ETFs led by those favored by the national team saw nearly \(24 billion of inflows in a week.\)
不过，与“国家队”活动相比，这一规模仍属温和：在四月份的抛售期间，由“国家队”偏好的股票型ETF在一周内录得近240亿美元的资金流入。

\*Russian Government is preparing measures to support the steel industry. The list of measures to support steelmakers facing weak demand and low prices may include increasing export duty on scrap and easing the burden of excise duty on liquid steel: Kommersant
\*俄罗斯政府正准备采取措施支持钢铁行业。据《生意人报》报道，为了支持面临需求疲软和价格低迷的钢铁制造商，措施清单可能包括提高废钢出口关税以及减轻液态钢消费税负担。

\*Codelco's Pacheco Says 6m Tons/Yr Chile Copper Output Hard: DF...Codelco Chairman Maximo Pacheco said that amid stagnant Chilean copper production, reaching six million tons of annual output by 2027 is a challenge. After 20 years of copper production being stuck at 5.5m tons, Pacheco said at a mining event that he disagrees with the vice president of government agency Cochilco, who has said the country can reach 6m tons: Diario Financiero. SQM- Codelco deal is advancing, Pacheco said: Diario Financiero. Pacheco said deal to be signed this week with BHP for Anillo project exploration: Diario Financiero. Anglo American and Codelco will hopefully sign common mining agreement in coming weeks, Pacheco said: Diario Financiero

\*Codelco董事长MaximoPacheco表示，智利铜产量停滞不前，要在2027年实现年产600万吨铜的目标具有挑战性。据《金融日报》报道，在铜产量连续20年停留在550万吨后，Pacheco在一次矿业活动中表示，他不同意智利国家铜业委员会（Cochilco）副主席的观点——后者认为该国可以实现600万吨的产量。Pacheco称，SQM与Codelco的交易正在推进中：《金融日报》。他还表示，本周将与必和必拓（BHP）签署Anillo项目勘探协议：《金融日报》。Pacheco称，安格鲁美洲公司（Anglo American）与Codelco有望在未来几周签署共同采矿协议：《金融日报》。
Exhibit 2:GS Metals and Mining commodity and FX forecasts
